{"tid":398304,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[畫圖]召喚3DJJ","createTime":"2017-09-13T05:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T11:00:40.000Z","uid":127705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"54ecb5dae7bb6d01f1df78092bb1d37a7df43746","tid":398304,"uid":127705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:46:07.000Z","msg":"小妹想學3D畫圖，但係零知識 (識Autocad)<br />\n想問下各位畫開3D圖既巴打，<br />\n我見到市面上都有幾款學<br />\nSketchup, 3ds Max, Autocad 3D, solidworks<br />\n<br />\n邊款係最common?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋我想問如果係呢兩個範疇，又應該揀乜？<br />\n-Construction<br />\n-Product design<br />\n<br />\n同埋我想入行做2D/3D drafting，到底學咩最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9adcde5c1ebf70bcd15bcac22f04659ed6a99e0a","tid":398304,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:41:05.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4f4ab0f0fb066bfedf85de80231c64cf8e62f721","tid":398304,"uid":127705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:13:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39529f500ee8f4c87b102120acac4c95a6039e7d","tid":398304,"uid":127705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490ea838aefbb6b7c8e55dc63e86d92478d3ad29","tid":398304,"uid":56618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:46:17.000Z","msg":"3d有個叫Revit"},{"pid":"e85acd8bb258e909fea55a16fbbf9259a4daa812","tid":398304,"uid":51039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:49:37.000Z","msg":"依d要搵課程讀下喎<br />\n自己學真係頂唔撚緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時中學自學3ds max參加表賽差d想死"},{"pid":"c39cb15aec74a7fbd461b4981eb0da022a14aa81","tid":398304,"uid":51039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依d要搵課程讀下喎<br />\n自己學真係頂唔撚緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時中學自學3ds max參加<span style=\"color: red;\">比</span>賽差d想死</blockquote>"},{"pid":"686ca10c00cd89106f974c3da14c50ad38090f81","tid":398304,"uid":61752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:26:00.000Z","msg":"Zbrush<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4HkH3xrJ7Xs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4HkH3xrJ7Xs&d=Fiapx9xV0uLnJffjTeDtIl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=4da2732b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4HkH3xrJ7Xs</a>"},{"pid":"849989fdc0ae18bd2d614a225f34bc3703a77de5","tid":398304,"uid":127705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3d有個叫Revit</blockquote><br />\n好用？common??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c466eeb33eb59bca6c7969755b80b5cb7306dd","tid":398304,"uid":55725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:50:18.000Z","msg":"blender 好似都唔錯<br />\nunreal engine youtube channel 都有教點implement"},{"pid":"7dc128de9b3d272e59f34fc2c463369df599ce50","tid":398304,"uid":133383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T07:57:41.000Z","msg":"3D建模因應產品要求不同,現時主流分两大類,NURBS,Polygon mesh.兩種建模方法有很大分別.<br />\n<br />\n工業產品設計：CATIA,Creo Parametric(改名前Pro_Enginner),NX UG,Solidworks 老牌知名公司,工業主流軟件.基於NURBS(非均勻有理B樣條),參數化實體建模,功能多樣(CAD,CAM,CAE).除Solidworks(CAD,CAE)價錢較低外,其它幾十至過百非常昂貴.<br />\n<br />\n動畫,生物模型：Autodesk 3D MAX,MAYA,Cinema 4D,ZBrush.基於Polygon mesh(多邊形網格)建模<br />\n<br />\nCAID：Rhinoceros,Autodesk Alias 產品前期設計,概念設計,CLASS A SURFACE<br />\n<br />\n建築,室內：Autodesk 3D MAX DESGIN,AUTOCAD,AutoCAD Architecture<br />\n<br />\n時裝設計..........等等.<br />\n還有很多細分項目軟件,五花八門,所知有限,沒能盡錄.<br />\n<br />\n如何選擇：睇你自己興趣或是那一行工作去決定,不作意見.<br />\n先指聲明：本身不是設計師,工程師,大學生.因從事五金模具,CNC加工多年,須耍接觸到Pro_Enginner,Mastercam,autocad,solidworks這類軟件,略懂皮毛,提供少少參考資料.有錯歡迎指證."},{"pid":"a6639f68661e608c735faa9bc77e4ba5b788b771","tid":398304,"uid":117896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T08:00:57.000Z","msg":"CAD LA唔洗諗 REVIT都開始HIT"},{"pid":"d7059a17d9231a4dc4d0bcab1188802806af3f3c","tid":398304,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T08:36:54.000Z","msg":"淘寶Solidworks有冇伏，好似聽過有巴打用"},{"pid":"d186b18cb4cc6bb815cd1f6875dbb1790e3512b9","tid":398304,"uid":133383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:04:48.000Z","msg":"補充少少:還有近年興起3D PRINT,是以前玩具手板模型的快速成型技術(Rapid Prototyping),演化出來新技術,以更平,占更小空間,平民化到家用層面上.<br />\n沒親身玩過."},{"pid":"454a38eecbb36b9543bd8b06eb43898b8a5a6a2c","tid":398304,"uid":127705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T19:51:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3D建模因應產品要求不同,現時主流分两大類,NURBS,Polygon mesh.兩種建模方法有很大分別.<br />\n<br />\n工業產品設計：CATIA,Creo Parametric(改名前Pro_Enginner),NX UG,Solidworks 老牌知名公司,工業主流軟件.基於NURBS(非均勻有理B樣條),參數化實體建模,功能多樣(CAD,CAM,CAE).除Solidworks(CAD,CAE)價錢較低外,其它幾十至過百非常昂貴.<br />\n<br />\n動畫,生物模型：Autodesk 3D MAX,MAYA,Cinema 4D,ZBrush.基於Polygon mesh(多邊形網格)建模<br />\n<br />\nCAID：Rhinoceros,Autodesk Alias 產品前期設計,概念設計,CLASS A SURFACE<br />\n<br />\n建築,室內：Autodesk 3D MAX DESGIN,AUTOCAD,AutoCAD Architecture<br />\n<br />\n時裝設計..........等等.<br />\n還有很多細分項目軟件,五花八門,所知有限,沒能盡錄.<br />\n<br />\n如何選擇：睇你自己興趣或是那一行工作去決定,不作意見.<br />\n先指聲明：本身不是設計師,工程師,大學生.因從事五金模具,CNC加工多年,須耍接觸到Pro_Enginner,Mastercam,autocad,solidworks這類軟件,略懂皮毛,提供少少參考資料.有錯歡迎指證.</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好專業，等我睇下先"},{"pid":"69b3a8963fd5a524ba14651a9455d3c6aff1e956","tid":398304,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T20:10:19.000Z","msg":"識 MAYA, Alias, Solidworks, 3D max, PRO/E, UG, rhino<br />\n工程類平價首選 solidworks,"},{"pid":"593f93072ae4ec220cf452f6d798b7be3c6e6a2b","tid":398304,"uid":8377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:26:08.000Z","msg":"我用開Blender <br />\nBlender 功能強大 又媲美Maya , 3D max 呢d 昂貴3D 軟體<br />\n<br />\n最最最重要係 Blender 係免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4917e3ea81a69074f98101cc618ce5a5ed3650dd","tid":398304,"uid":192587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:00:40.000Z","msg":"自己本黎就用開solidwork畫工程件，根住機緣巧合下intern搵到份畫圖既工（政府），就學埋用3ds max。<br />\n<br />\n兩個程式上既畫圖概念/方式都幾唔同，不過要學其實唔係點畫樣野，係點用個程式，用過電腦繪圖你就明我講咩，Youtube Google永遠都幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n建議冇基礎既話可以從一d簡單既幾何圖形開始，好似櫃呀、桌呀咁，之後再到一d有流線型、甚至唔係硬物既野。<br />\n<br />\n如果就咁畫覺得尺寸未掌握到，可以上網搵圖，再plug-in 就blueprint。"}]}